      <title>Roku 报告称，由于竞争激烈，季度亏损超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/roku-forecasts-first-quarter-revenue-above-estimates-2024-02-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Roku 周四公布的第四季度亏损超出预期，原因是该公司面临财力雄厚的竞争对手的激烈竞争以及视频流媒体客户支出疲软，导致其股价在盘中交易中下跌 15%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/roku-forecasts-first-quarter-revenue-above-estimates-2024-02-15/</guid>
